SIMPLE: unclose
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unclose
<hw>Unclose</hw>  <def>See <er>close</er>.</def>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unclose
<hw>Un*close"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>close</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To open; to
separate the parts of; <as>as, to <ex>unclose</ex> a letter; to
<ex>unclose</ex> one's eyes</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To disclose; to lay open; to reveal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unclosed</ent>⟦br⟧
